text: The L7 medics here were amazing. The audio medic extremely patient with me for even though i was unsure if i had responded to the correct audio que. The dispense medic was fast with my medication and even gave me a clear explanation about my medication. And lastly the medic at the front counter was very helpful when i had many queries. Had a great experience overall throughout all the times that I have been here.
Friendly and helpful staff overall. But someone flooded the toilet. It was a bit challenging to pee without my fire hose being submerged in the overflowing urinal, but manageable overall.
Amazing place and amazing staff! One of the guys even asked me out during lunch at frontier. Had i not said yes, i would have been so lonely for the whole of Uni. Best. Decision. EVERR!
